               <msContents>
                  <summary>Praises of Mary, ውዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡; Gate of Light, አንቀጸ፡ ብርሃን፡; Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡; Image of Sinoda, መልክአ፡ ሲኖዳ፡, produced in the Government Scriptorium</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="33r" facs="002">Fols 1r–33r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas">Wǝddāse
                                                  Māryām</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="33v" to="46v" facs="035">Fols 33v–46v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1113Anqasa">ʾAnqaṣa
                                                  bǝrhān</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="47r" to="58v" facs="048">Fols 47r–58v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2835RepCh119">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Mikāʾel</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="59r" to="66v" facs="060">Fols 59r–66v</locus>
                     <title>Image of Sinoda, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክአ፡ ሲኖዳ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ነጐድጓድ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወለእለ፡ ኬፋ፡ አቢያጺሁ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ በትርሲተ፡ጸጋ፡ ወሞገስ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
